data.description: Charming Carlisle condo in Goose hollow!With its updated features and prime location, this condo presents an exceptional opportunity for urban living at its finest.- Expansive eleven-foot ceilings create a sense of grandeur and spaciousness.- The interior has been tastefully updated, including flooring, cabinetry, fixtures, and appliances, ensuring a modern and stylish living experience.- The well-appointed kitchen with sleek quartz countertops and a convenient breakfast bar, perfect for casual dining or hosting guests.- Take advantage of the incredible rooftop community area, where you can enjoy beautiful city and mountain views. Great for social gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day.- A storage unit is included for all your storing needs! - The location is a commuter's dream, with close proximity to light rail stations, allowing for easy access to all that downtown has to offer. Experience the vibrant city life, dining, shopping, and entertainment options just moments away. Also easy access to Portland state university, Providence Park, and Multnomah Athletic Club!
